title: 6: Breakups, Manslaughter, and Getting Fired ft. Ali
description:
Joined by her once childhood enemy, Sofia and Ali discuss how to get over a breakup - even if it means moving to another state. (P.S. relocating is scary stuff and these besties are ready to talk about their own experiences. Nothing crosses the line with these two, even when Ali runs over her ex-boyfriend with her car or when Sofia needed corrective surgery in Vegas. The duo recounts their most intimate and idiotic stories to date. True friendship means forever.
